starter_deck_guid = 'bc69b7'

next_round_button_params = {
  click_function = 'nextClicked',
  function_owner = self,
  label = 'Next Round',
  position={-0.1,0.1,-1},
  rotation = {0,180,0},
  width = 650,
  height = 200,
  font_size = 100
}

function onLoad()
  special_deck_zone = getObjectFromGUID(special_deck_zone_guid)
  special_deck_zone.createButton(next_round_button_params)
end

function nextClicked()
  starter_deck = getObjectFromGUID(starter_deck_guid)
  starter_deck.shuffle()
  broadcastToAll("Here!!")
  -- pos = starter_deck.getPosition()
  card = starter_deck.takeObject({
    position = {x=-7, y=3, z=-6.4},
    top      = true,
    flip     = true,
    smooth   = true,
  })
  card = starter_deck.takeObject({
    position = {x=-0.88, y=3, z=-6.4},
    top      = true,
    flip     = true,
    smooth   = true,
  })
  card = starter_deck.takeObject({
    position = {x=5.22, y=3, z=-6.4},
    top      = true,
    flip     = true,
    smooth   = true,
  })

end

ObjectStates.Description: Use this checker to find the coordinates on the table
ObjectStates.LuaScript:
self.setName("The Position Checker")
self.setDescription("Use this checker to find the coordinates on the table")
self.createButton({
  click_function = 'check_position',
  function_owner = self,
  label = 'Check',
  position = {0.1,0.23,2},
  rotation = {0,0,0},
  width = 500,
  height = 500,
  font_size = 100,
})

function check_position()
    pos = self.getPosition()
    pos_str = "x: "..pos[1]..", y: "..pos[2]..",\nz: "..pos[3].."."
    broadcastToAll(pos_str)
    print(pos_str)
    setNotes(pos_str)
end
